  "detailed_description": "<h1>Discord</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/e399f42dbd060d9e1c4f7ff3940d135d.poster.avif?t=1770640898\" width=620 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/e399f42dbd060d9e1c4f7ff3940d135d.webm?t=1770640898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play CTHULOOT online with <strong>up to 4 players</strong> via RemotePlay Together and <strong>only 1 copy of the game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/fe538e6daa05e3bc581fc875abbd67e7.poster.avif?t=1770640898\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/fe538e6daa05e3bc581fc875abbd67e7.webm?t=1770640898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE GREAT OLD ONES ARE CALLING!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Round up your friends to form a gang of semi-competent looters in search of the relics lost by the Great Old Ones. Just be careful not to invoke them again!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/96fbff71c148e983360481231112f4a9.poster.avif?t=1770640898\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/96fbff71c148e983360481231112f4a9.webm?t=1770640898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COOP MULTIPLAYER GAME TO PLAY WITH YOUR FRIENDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore mysterious realms in the liminal space between reality and madness, and collect mad loot along the way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/c235af52eaa220693ef816ec23b767f5.poster.avif?t=1770640898\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/c235af52eaa220693ef816ec23b767f5.webm?t=1770640898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIND AND COLLECT ANCESTRAL RELICS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Lord Morgaz'han regain his rightful place among the Great Old Ones with the power of the treasures you'll find. Draw on his collection of supernatural watches to acquire new skills! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/1bb0097151a562da9f76e44bf8050fd8.poster.avif?t=1770640898\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/1bb0097151a562da9f76e44bf8050fd8.webm?t=1770640898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WILL YOU STILL BE FRIENDS WHEN IT'S ALL OVER?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show off your skills as a looter, and don't lose anything along the way if you don't want to drag your team down!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play CTHULOOT online with <strong>up to 4 players</strong> via RemotePlay Together and <strong>only 1 copy of the game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/fe538e6daa05e3bc581fc875abbd67e7.poster.avif?t=1770640898\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/fe538e6daa05e3bc581fc875abbd67e7.webm?t=1770640898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE GREAT OLD ONES ARE CALLING!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Round up your friends to form a gang of semi-competent looters in search of the relics lost by the Great Old Ones. Just be careful not to invoke them again!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/96fbff71c148e983360481231112f4a9.poster.avif?t=1770640898\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/96fbff71c148e983360481231112f4a9.webm?t=1770640898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COOP MULTIPLAYER GAME TO PLAY WITH YOUR FRIENDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore mysterious realms in the liminal space between reality and madness, and collect mad loot along the way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/c235af52eaa220693ef816ec23b767f5.poster.avif?t=1770640898\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/c235af52eaa220693ef816ec23b767f5.webm?t=1770640898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIND AND COLLECT ANCESTRAL RELICS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Lord Morgaz'han regain his rightful place among the Great Old Ones with the power of the treasures you'll find. Draw on his collection of supernatural watches to acquire new skills! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/1bb0097151a562da9f76e44bf8050fd8.poster.avif?t=1770640898\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283410/extras/1bb0097151a562da9f76e44bf8050fd8.webm?t=1770640898\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WILL YOU STILL BE FRIENDS WHEN IT'S ALL OVER?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show off your skills as a looter, and don't lose anything along the way if you don't want to drag your team down!</p>",
